  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    IntensityPerPixelMetric
    A simple Metric that quantifies the total intensity in a region of interest divided by the size of that region of interest.
    Measurement
    Represents a single scalar measurement made based on the quantification of an image.
    Metric
    A quantitative measurement on an image or set of images with an associated mask of regions of interest.
    Quantification
    Represents the result of quantifying an image.
